docs.title: Become a sponsor
docs.text: By joining the Insiders program, you'll get immediate access to the latest features while also helping support the ongoing development of CUMULATIVE. Thanks to our awesome sponsors, this project is actively maintained and kept in good shape.

docs.title: How to join the Insiders program
docs.text: Please send a short email to michele.dallachiesa@sigforge.com, Thank You.
